25:14.000 --> 25:15.000
and that person,

25:15.000 --> 25:16.000
would they be saying,

25:16.000 --> 25:17.000
oh yeah,

25:17.000 --> 25:18.000
enjoy your senses while you,

25:18.000 --> 25:19.000
while you're still alive?

25:19.000 --> 25:21.000
They might be telling others that.

25:21.000 --> 25:22.000
Well, they might,

25:22.000 --> 25:23.000
oh see,

