And you know that,

25:32.000 --> 25:33.000
for yourself,

25:33.000 --> 25:34.000
everybody experienced

25:34.000 --> 25:36.000
that more or less,

25:36.000 --> 25:37.000
when you're healthy,

25:37.000 --> 25:38.000
you don't care,

25:38.000 --> 25:39.000
when you get sick,

25:39.000 --> 25:41.000
then you get all really worried,

25:41.000 --> 25:42.000
and then you're,

25:42.000 --> 25:43.000
oh,

25:43.000 --> 25:44.000
and you got sick

25:44.000 --> 25:45.000
because of your stupidity

25:45.000 --> 25:46.000
or foolishness,

25:46.000 --> 25:48.000
and then you make all those grand,

25:48.000 --> 25:49.000
they think, oh,

25:49.000 --> 25:50.000
never did that again.

25:50.000 --> 25:51.000
And then you recover,

25:51.000 --> 25:52.000
and then you're back

25:52.000 --> 25:53.000
to the old ways

25:53.000 --> 25:54.000
you completely forgot.

25:54.000 --> 25:55.000
It's pure intoxication.

25:55.000 --> 25:57.000
It's what you have at the time.

25:57.000 --> 25:58.000
It's like,

25:58.000 --> 25:59.000
complete,

25:59.000 --> 26:00.000
like the mindfulness.

26:00.000 --> 26:02.000
Absence.

26:02.000 --> 26:05.000
And saying,

26:05.000 --> 26:07.000
you make grand plans

26:07.000 --> 26:08.000
and projects,

26:08.000 --> 26:10.000
and ideas,

26:10.000 --> 26:11.000
and hopes,

26:11.000 --> 26:12.000
and whatever else,

26:12.000 --> 26:13.000
just because you assume

26:13.000 --> 26:14.000
you will live forever,

26:14.000 --> 26:15.000
you assume your life

26:15.000 --> 26:17.000
will last for a long time.

26:17.000 --> 26:19.000
And if you stop

26:19.000 --> 26:21.000
and think about that assumption,

26:21.000 --> 26:22.000
it's completely gratuitous.

26:22.000 --> 26:24.000
As every assumption is,

26:24.000 --> 26:25.000
but this one,

26:25.000 --> 26:35.000
it really can hit you.

26:35.000 --> 26:43.000
So, as Buddha said,

26:43.000 --> 26:45.000
even if somebody went for,

26:45.000 --> 26:47.000
and they don't achieve anything,

26:47.000 --> 26:51.000
but they don't disrupt the state,

26:51.000 --> 26:53.000
they keep the rules,

26:53.000 --> 26:56.000
and they keep trying to practice.

26:56.000 --> 26:57.000
Even if they don't get anywhere,

26:57.000 --> 26:59.000
even if they spend every single day,

26:59.000 --> 27:01.000
for the rest of their life,

27:01.000 --> 27:03.000
in tears, in pain,

27:03.000 --> 27:05.000
imposed by the restraint,

27:05.000 --> 27:08.000
it's still better than going back.

27:08.000 --> 27:09.000
Why?

27:09.000 --> 27:11.000
Because you've been around so long,

27:11.000 --> 27:12.000
so many times,

27:12.000 --> 27:13.000
it's spending

27:13.000 --> 27:15.000
a third of your lifetime now,

27:15.000 --> 27:17.000
crying in pain,

27:17.000 --> 27:19.000
but holding that restraint,

27:19.000 --> 27:22.000
will actually contribute much more,

27:22.000 --> 27:25.000
than just giving in to the senses.

27:25.000 --> 27:26.000
And then, at the same time,

27:26.000 --> 27:27.000
we stop thinking,

27:27.000 --> 27:29.000
well, it's impossible to spend every single day,

27:29.000 --> 27:31.000
for the rest of your life,

27:31.000 --> 27:33.000
in tears, in pain.

27:33.000 --> 27:34.000
No matter how great that pain is,

27:34.000 --> 27:37.000
it will fade.

27:37.000 --> 27:40.000
But if you're ready for every single day of pain,

27:40.000 --> 28:07.000
anything less than that will be a blessing.

28:07.000 --> 28:10.000
And people, nobody likes this strain,

28:10.000 --> 28:13.000
because it feels like a chore.

28:13.000 --> 28:17.000
It feels like an effort.

28:17.000 --> 28:19.000
And it feels like that,

28:19.000 --> 28:21.000
only from the point of view,

28:21.000 --> 28:26.000
where your sensuality feels effortless.

28:26.000 --> 28:29.000
Now, the actual gratification of the senses,

28:29.000 --> 28:31.000
might feel effortless,

28:31.000 --> 28:34.000
but it never comes on its own.

28:34.000 --> 28:37.000
It always comes with a price.

28:37.000 --> 28:39.000
And it's not seeing the connection

28:39.000 --> 28:42.000
between sensuality and gratification

28:42.000 --> 28:46.000
and the price and the toll it takes.

28:46.000 --> 28:48.000
You reflect on the connection long enough,

28:48.000 --> 28:49.000
and it would become apparent

28:49.000 --> 28:51.000
because it is there.

28:51.000 --> 28:52.000
And then you realize,

28:52.000 --> 28:54.000
it's much harder,

28:54.000 --> 28:56.000
much more taxing,

28:56.000 --> 28:58.000
much more,

28:58.000 --> 29:00.000
much more of a chore,

29:00.000 --> 29:02.000
to be following your senses,

29:02.000 --> 29:04.000
and enjoying them,

29:04.000 --> 29:08.000
then saying no to the whole thing.

29:08.000 --> 29:11.000
But that connection needs to be well on long enough

29:11.000 --> 29:12.000
until it becomes apparent,

29:12.000 --> 29:13.000
because it's not apparent,

29:13.000 --> 29:15.000
because if it were apparent so easily,

29:15.000 --> 29:20.000
everybody would be free from sensuality.

29:20.000 --> 29:22.000
And you can start with a simple reflection of,

29:22.000 --> 29:25.000
if you are a layperson,

29:25.000 --> 29:29.000
living a household life,

29:29.000 --> 29:32.000
enjoying the pleasures of your senses,

29:32.000 --> 29:35.000
means pleasant pastes,

29:35.000 --> 29:37.000
touches sounds,

29:37.000 --> 29:39.000
finding a pleasant wife,

29:39.000 --> 29:41.000
or a girlfriend,

29:41.000 --> 29:44.000
living a pleasant life.

29:44.000 --> 29:47.000
How do you achieve that?

29:47.000 --> 29:49.000
You need to work.

29:49.000 --> 29:51.000
You need to earn.

29:51.000 --> 29:53.000
You need to really

29:53.000 --> 29:55.000
put up with stuff you don't like,

29:55.000 --> 29:57.000
very often.

29:57.000 --> 29:59.000
You might find the work you like,

29:59.000 --> 30:01.000
you might be your own boss,

30:01.000 --> 30:03.000
but then you have to protect it.

30:03.000 --> 30:04.000
You have to fend off.

30:04.000 --> 30:06.000
People who want the same.

30:06.000 --> 30:07.000
People who cheated,

30:07.000 --> 30:08.000
people who lie,

30:08.000 --> 30:10.000
and people want to take things away from you.

30:10.000 --> 30:13.000
So there's always that risk.

30:13.000 --> 30:16.000
Then you're committing your life to it.

30:16.000 --> 30:20.000
You're spending 90% of doing things

30:20.000 --> 30:22.000
you don't want,

30:22.000 --> 30:25.000
just so you get that 5% enjoyment.

30:25.000 --> 30:29.000
It doesn't feel directly related to it,

30:29.000 --> 30:30.000
and that's the ignorance,

30:30.000 --> 30:32.000
obscuring it.

30:32.000 --> 30:34.000
But if you realize that it's impossible

30:34.000 --> 30:36.000
to have enjoyment,

30:36.000 --> 30:40.000
without 95% of pain revolving around it,

30:40.000 --> 30:42.000
directly or indirectly,

30:42.000 --> 30:46.000
you realize that enjoyment is not worth it.

30:46.000 --> 30:48.000
And that's when the Buddha talks about

30:48.000 --> 30:50.000
seeing the danger

30:50.000 --> 30:53.000
in the sensuality.

30:53.000 --> 30:56.000
So by choosing to pursue

30:56.000 --> 30:57.000
the ways of the senses,

30:57.000 --> 31:00.000
which is basically choosing to have family,

31:00.000 --> 31:02.000
children, wives or husbands,

31:02.000 --> 31:05.000
whatever else,

31:05.000 --> 31:07.000
living that kind of life,

31:07.000 --> 31:11.000
you accept that whole central domain

31:11.000 --> 31:13.000
with these things pertain,

31:13.000 --> 31:15.000
with these things are,

31:15.000 --> 31:17.000
which means you don't practice restraint,

31:17.000 --> 31:20.000
but you practice pursuit.

31:20.000 --> 31:22.000
And that's a form of commitment.

31:22.000 --> 31:24.000
Pursuing your senses is a form of commitment,

31:24.000 --> 31:26.000
but then you realize,

31:26.000 --> 31:29.000
by accepting, by engaging in that pursuit,

31:29.000 --> 31:31.000
you make yourself liable

31:31.000 --> 31:33.000
to a great loss.

31:33.000 --> 31:36.000
So say, you commit yourself to a pursuit

31:36.000 --> 31:38.000
of having a family,

31:38.000 --> 31:40.000
having children.

31:40.000 --> 31:43.000
Well, now that you have family and children,

31:43.000 --> 31:45.000
you have to work harder for them.

31:45.000 --> 31:48.000
For the food, for the clothing, for the school.

31:48.000 --> 31:50.000
What if they get sick?

31:50.000 --> 31:52.000
What if they die on you?

31:52.000 --> 31:55.000
You spent 20, 30 years,

31:55.000 --> 31:58.000
cultivating, investing in those things,

31:58.000 --> 32:00.000
dedicating your whole life,

32:00.000 --> 32:02.000
praising your children,

32:02.000 --> 32:04.000
then they turn away on you,

32:04.000 --> 32:06.000
or they die, or an accident happened,

32:06.000 --> 32:08.000
and they just snatched away

32:08.000 --> 32:10.000
in a second,

32:10.000 --> 32:13.000
and you have not had say in that

32:13.000 --> 32:15.000
from the beginning.

32:15.000 --> 32:17.000
Like, from the day one,

32:17.000 --> 32:19.000
you have no say in the destiny of your child.

32:19.000 --> 32:21.000
Well, you have no say in your own destiny,

32:21.000 --> 32:23.000
but you have ignored that

32:23.000 --> 32:25.000
when you decided to pursue the senses.

32:25.000 --> 32:27.000
But if you reflect on that,

32:27.000 --> 32:31.000
you realize that even the pursuit of the senses

32:31.000 --> 32:33.000
is actually completely out of your hands.

32:33.000 --> 32:36.000
That's why the suitors compare it to climbing a tree.

32:36.000 --> 32:39.000
Oh, you see the ripe mangoes

32:39.000 --> 32:41.000
on the tree, so you climb the tree

32:41.000 --> 32:43.000
to eat them, to enjoy them.

32:43.000 --> 32:46.000
And then somebody else while you're on top of that tree

32:46.000 --> 32:48.000
comes, and he can't climb the tree,

32:48.000 --> 32:50.000
so he decides to cut it.

32:50.000 --> 32:52.000
While you're still on the top,

32:52.000 --> 32:54.000
he doesn't see or he doesn't care.

32:54.000 --> 32:56.000
You chop the tree, you fall down, break in there,

32:56.000 --> 32:58.000
and you're done.

32:58.000 --> 33:00.000
And pursue the senses

33:00.000 --> 33:02.000
exposes you to that,

33:02.000 --> 33:04.000
means going down, or climbing up the tree,

33:04.000 --> 33:06.000
off a kind,

33:06.000 --> 33:08.000
or the other,

33:08.000 --> 33:10.000
and something might come at a direct cross-purpose

33:10.000 --> 33:12.000
and just snatch it away from you.

33:12.000 --> 33:14.000
Be it an accident, being other people,

33:14.000 --> 33:16.000
being both.

33:16.000 --> 33:17.000
Who knows?

33:17.000 --> 33:20.000
The point is, the exposure is there.

33:20.000 --> 33:24.000
So there is the inherent danger in that pursuit.

33:24.000 --> 33:28.000
So you realize that danger is 95% of luck.

33:28.000 --> 33:31.000
Easy worth risking your life,

33:31.000 --> 33:35.000
putting your head on a chopping block

33:35.000 --> 33:38.000
when there is a good chance of accident falling down,

33:38.000 --> 33:42.000
just so you get that 5% thrill.

33:42.000 --> 33:44.000
And in this worth,

33:44.000 --> 33:46.000
that gratification is worth

33:46.000 --> 33:48.000
for as long as you don't establish that connection

33:48.000 --> 33:49.000
between the two.

33:49.000 --> 33:53.000
I, for as long as you don't see the danger in centrality.

33:53.000 --> 33:55.000
You establish the connection

33:55.000 --> 33:57.000
and then the danger became apparent.

33:57.000 --> 33:58.000
The visible.

33:58.000 --> 33:59.000
The mind turned away.

33:59.000 --> 34:00.000
Spear is the passion.

34:00.000 --> 34:02.000
As the suit is described.

34:02.000 --> 34:07.000
Oh, like the disgust became real.

34:07.000 --> 34:09.000
This is danger.

34:09.000 --> 34:11.000
This is not like mind turned away.

34:11.000 --> 34:12.000
Never to go back to it.

34:12.000 --> 34:13.000
Why?

34:13.000 --> 34:14.000
Because it is like that.

34:14.000 --> 34:16.000
Essentiality and gratification

34:16.000 --> 34:19.000
would not inherently be dangerous

34:19.000 --> 34:20.000
and risky,

34:20.000 --> 34:25.000
and much more revolving around pain

34:25.000 --> 34:27.000
in this satisfaction.

34:27.000 --> 34:30.000
If it wouldn't be inherently that,

34:30.000 --> 34:32.000
then it wouldn't be unholy.

34:32.000 --> 34:35.000
And that certainly freedom from it would not be possible.

34:35.000 --> 34:39.000
But because it is inherently dangerous, risky,

34:39.000 --> 34:41.000
and not worthy,

34:41.000 --> 34:43.000
it is inherently like that.

34:43.000 --> 34:46.000
But dwelling on that freedom from it is possible.

34:46.000 --> 34:48.000
And then you realize,

34:48.000 --> 34:52.000
saying no as a formal restraint to centrality,

34:52.000 --> 34:54.000
it's 5% of effort,

34:54.000 --> 34:56.000
95% of peace,

34:56.000 --> 34:58.000
and it's well worth it.

34:58.000 --> 35:00.000
And that's when you find,

35:00.000 --> 35:04.000
when a person finds pleasure over renunciation,

35:04.000 --> 35:08.000
like actually you experience pleasure

35:08.000 --> 35:11.000
by being, by recognizing strength

35:11.000 --> 35:13.000
that you have of saying no,

35:13.000 --> 35:15.000
not being you are stronger than senses,

35:15.000 --> 35:17.000
senses are not stronger than you.

35:21.000 --> 35:23.000
There's also a view that you will actually

35:23.000 --> 35:26.000
through those challenges in life.

35:26.000 --> 35:28.000
If you're having a family in the child,

35:28.000 --> 35:30.000
you will get to know yourself.

35:30.000 --> 35:31.000
Yeah.

35:31.000 --> 35:32.000
You will evolve.

35:32.000 --> 35:34.000
You will evolve in a way,

35:34.000 --> 35:37.000
in a discovering different ways

35:37.000 --> 35:39.000
of pursuing the senses.

35:39.000 --> 35:42.000
But whether you evolve this way or that way,

35:42.000 --> 35:43.000
bottom line is,

35:43.000 --> 35:46.000
it's still within the nature of pursuing the senses,

35:46.000 --> 35:49.000
and that's still within the nature of their danger and risk.

35:49.000 --> 35:53.000
Does any evolving that you do

35:53.000 --> 35:55.000
will be within that?

35:55.000 --> 35:58.000
It's basically like going in a muddy swamp

35:58.000 --> 36:00.000
and finding different ways

36:00.000 --> 36:04.000
to wash yourself with a muddy water.

36:04.000 --> 36:07.000
No matter how liberated your ways become,

36:07.000 --> 36:10.000
it's still filled with water.

36:10.000 --> 36:13.000
Means you'll never be clean.

36:14.000 --> 36:17.000
Evolving the same way.

36:17.000 --> 36:20.000
Evolving.

36:20.000 --> 36:23.000
Like, you can be in prison.

36:23.000 --> 36:26.000
In prison, behind a low door.

36:26.000 --> 36:29.000
Sure, you can evolve in that environment.

36:29.000 --> 36:31.000
Whatever evolving you do,

36:31.000 --> 36:33.000
it will be evolving in the prison.

36:33.000 --> 36:35.000
But you really want to be out of the prison.

36:35.000 --> 36:38.000
It's better to be uninvolved out of the prison

36:38.000 --> 36:41.000
than involved in very common sense in the prison.

36:41.000 --> 36:43.000
Because that's not really involvement.

36:43.000 --> 36:45.000
It's just a further proliferation.

36:45.000 --> 36:47.000
And it's people say that they never say

36:47.000 --> 36:49.000
for any other sense,

36:49.000 --> 36:52.000
any other purpose than a purpose of justifying their pursuit

36:52.000 --> 36:55.000
of the senses upon which they already decided.

36:55.000 --> 36:59.000
But now they need to keep justifying it.

36:59.000 --> 37:01.000
And sure, you can.

37:01.000 --> 37:03.000
But you do that to others

37:03.000 --> 37:05.000
because you might feel guilty,

37:05.000 --> 37:11.000
or you might feel watched or judged.

37:11.000 --> 37:14.000
So you justify yourself.

37:14.000 --> 37:16.000
But basically,

37:16.000 --> 37:21.000
that's done already when you're deeply committed to the senses.

37:21.000 --> 37:24.000
So now you're just trying to make the best out of it.

37:24.000 --> 37:27.000
Cover up any doubt in regard to your choices,

37:27.000 --> 37:30.000
in regard to your commitment.

37:30.000 --> 37:33.000
Above all, observe all the responsibility for it.

37:33.000 --> 37:35.000
Oh, well, you know, I can't.

37:35.000 --> 37:38.000
