37:38.000 --> 37:41.000
Well, they were not given to you,

37:41.000 --> 37:44.000
like, you know, out of nowhere.

37:44.000 --> 37:46.000
You've chosen that.

37:46.000 --> 37:47.000
So basically what you're saying,

37:47.000 --> 37:50.000
you can't go forth because of the choices you make.

37:50.000 --> 37:53.000
